\n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link|\n  |party      = Labour Party (UK)\n  |candidate  = [[Arthur Davidson (politician)|Arthur Davidson]]\n  |votes      = 12,548\n  |percentage = 33.6\n  |change     = +0.8\n}}\n{{Election box majority|\n  |votes      = 12,225\n  |percentage = 32.8\n  |change     =\n}}\n{{Election box turnout|\n  |votes      = 37,321\n  |percentage = 67.7\n  |change     =\n}}\n{{Election box hold with party link|\n  |winner     = Conservative Party (UK)\n  |swing      = \u22120.8\n}}\n{{Election box end}}\n{{Election box begin | title=[[1951 United Kingdom general election|General election 1951]]: Blackpool South<ref>http://tools.assembla.com/svn/grodt/uk/thc/files/marked_up/1951_marked_up.txt</ref>}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link|\n  |party      = Conservative Party (UK)\n  |candidate  = [[Roland Robinson, 1st Baron Martonmere|Roland Robinson]]\n  |votes      = 28,171\n  |percentage = 67.2\n  |change     = +9.3\n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link|\n  |party      = Labour Party (UK)\n  |candidate  = [[Kenneth Lomas]]\n  |votes      = 13,750\n  |percentage = 32.8\n  |change     = +2.1\n}}\n{{Election box majority|\n  |votes      = 14,421\n  |percentage = 34.4\n  |change     =\n}}\n{{Election box turnout|\n  |votes      = 41,921\n  |percentage = 75.0\n  |change     =\n}}\n{{Election box hold with party link|\n  |winner     = Conservative Party (UK)\n  |swing      = +3.6\n}}\n{{Election box end}}\n{{Election box begin | title=[[1950 United Kingdom general election|General election 1950]]: Blackpool South}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link|\n  |party      = Conservative Party (UK)\n  |candidate  = [[Roland Robinson, 1st Baron Martonmere|Roland Robinson]]\n  |votes      = 26,800\n  |percentage = 57.9\n  |change     = +1.1\n}}\n{{Election box candidate with party link|\n  |party      = Labour Party (UK)\n  |candidate  = E.A. Machin\n  |votes      = 14,190\n  |percentage = 30.7\n  |change     = +6.5\n}}\n{{Election 